libtest-www-mechanize-psgi-perl (0.36-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ upstream ]
  * New release.

  [ Salvatore Bonaccorso ]
  * Change Vcs-Git to canonical URI (git://anonscm.debian.org)

  [ Axel Beckert ]
  * debian/copyright: migrate pre-1.0 format to 1.0 using "cme fix
    dpkg-copyright"

  [ Jonas Smedegaard ]
  * Update copyright info:
    + Use issue tracker as preferred form oc contact.
    + Add alternate git source.
    + Use License-Grant and License-Reference fields.
      Thanks to Ben Finney.
    + Extend coverage for Debian packaging.
    + Tighten licensing for Debian packaging to GPL-3+.
  * Update watch file:
    + Bump to file format 4.
    + Watch MetaCPAN URL.
    + Mention gbp --uscan in usage comment.
  * Modernize git-buildpackage config: Filter any .git* file.
  * Add lintian overrides regarding license in License-Reference field.
    See bug#786450.
  * Bump debhelper compatibility level to 9.
  * Declare compliance with Debian Policy 3.9.8.
  * Modernize Vcs-* fields:
    + Use https URLs.
    + Use cgit browser
  * Drop CDBS get-orig-source target: Use gbp import-orig --uscan.
  * Modernize CDBS use:
    + Build-depend on licensecheck (not devscripts).
    + Relax to build-depend unversioned on cdbs.
  * Relax to build-depend unversioned on debhelper.

